title: Outback Trading Women's Matilda Waterproof Windproof Breathable Long Waxed Cotton Western Duster Coat
features: Made in the USA or Imported

WEATHERPROOF DUSTER - Designed to be a reliable companion for the toughest adventures, this the Matilda waxed cotton western duster features a waterproof construction that can withstand light drizzle and heavy rainfall

PERFECT FIT - Equipped with snap adjustable cuffs, leg straps and a drawstring waistband, this ladies' waterproof & breathable coat closely conforms to the body to offer a snug fit and help improve range of motion
DETACHABLE CAPE - This full-size long-sleeved raincoat with a corduroy collar and reinforced elbow patches incorporates a detachable cape that you can use for additional protection during a downpour

FUNCTIONAL RAINCOAT - This duster features dual entry hip pockets & an inside security pocket to store all your valuables; equipped with a storm flap, throat latch and inner zip, making it compatible with 48742 & 48743 vest liners
COTTON LINING - Furnished with soft cotton lining, this garment has a luxuriously soft interior that helps you keep warm and cozy throughout wear; it features yaffeta lined sleeves for a soft touch
description: Say hello to Matilda, our first Duster just for ladies! The Matilda comes in berry and bronze and is equipped with all of the great features of our unisex dusters such as a detachable cape, dual entry hip pockets, back riding gussets, leg straps, and dual snap closure but is made for a ladies frame.Whether you're a jockey, a farm worker, or simply an outdoor enthusiast, the Matilda Duster in Berry is guaranteed to be everyone's favorite gear.

- Waterproof & Breathable - Dual Snap Closure - Inside Security Pocket - Dual Entry Hip Pockets - Detachable Cape - Rear Saddle Gusset - Adjustable Leg Straps - Storm Flap - Throat Latch - Snap Adjustable Cuffs

Outback Trading Co. offers a great range of Duster Jackets. Dusters are the best protection during heavy rain or snow with their extended coverage. The Stockman, Low Rider and Packable Dusters are all in unisex sizing and we recommend you order a size smaller than your normal size. Be sure to look at the check sizing charts before placing an order.
